{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body><img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20260421/s00001/cca838efab69c39a008b753b4a8c639c.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%;border-radius:6px;margin-bottom:1em\">\n    <p>今晨（21日）8時許，一輛旅遊巴沿古洞路往新田方向，駛至文天祥公園對開時撞倒一名女途人，30多歲女事主昏迷不醒，由救護車送往北區醫院後證實不治。</p>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-21T03:46:30.247852+00:00","quality":{"score":0,"chars":72,"images":1,"source":"明報 本地","fallback":"none"}}